{
  "stem": "27747.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the [INAUDIBLE] said that she's going to help me, she's going to do copping.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Do you know what that is?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When you put-- copping is a little container, a glass container.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You put fire on the wood with alcohol, and you put it on the back and on the chest.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Apparently, that helped, because I survived, survived whether it was pneumonia or pleurisy, no one-- I couldn't remember.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And sure enough, that we heard that Hoszcza is freed, and that Miedzyrzecz is freed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they heard it from my-- from [INAUDIBLE] family, from my boss's family, that the Soviets are there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Soviets are there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when was this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was '44, in the winter of '44.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we-- we stayed in Rowne for awhile.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was told that there is a Jewish woman that lives in Rowne that came together with the army.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And since it was the Soviet government already, and I wasn't afraid to walk the streets, I came to see her.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she told me that she survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She's the only one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she survived close to Hoszcza, and she is now with the army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "While they were advancing, she came to the town of Rowne thinking that maybe some of her family she will find in Rowne, or in the towns near Rowne.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was looking for them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She told me that a few of the family survived, that she does not know anything about my mother or sister.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that she knows that the pharmacist is alive, and his wife.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to my-- to the family, I said that I'd like to go back to town.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They really tried to talk me out of it, and they said that I would be better off staying with them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
